  <name>Innerpix Lab</name>
  <summary>Privacy-first photo and video management</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Innerpix Lab manages, organizes, and optimizes photo and video
      collections with absolute privacy.  All processing is 100% local —
      no cloud, no telemetry, no external connections.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Exact and visual duplicate detection (SHA-256 + perceptual hashing)</li>
      <li>HEIC/JPG pair cleanup and Live Photo management</li>
      <li>Smart file organisation by date</li>
      <li>Batch renaming with EXIF-based date patterns</li>
      <li>Zero-byte file cleanup</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

